# ğŸ“Š E-Commerce Sales Dashboard (Power BI)

This project presents an interactive *E-Commerce Sales Dashboard* built in *Power BI* using raw Excel data.
It provides key insights into sales performance, product trends, profit analysis, and customer behavior through a clean and business-focused visualization.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The dashboard highlights key business metrics:

* *Total Sales*
* *Total Profit*
* *Profit Margin*
* *Total Orders*
* *Sales by Month*
* *Best & Worst Selling Products*
* *Sales by Region*
* *Customer Ratings*

It is designed for quick decision-making, performance tracking, and analytical storytelling.

---

## ğŸ¯ Objectives

* Analyze month-over-month sales and profit trends
* Identify top-performing and underperforming products
* Compare sales across geographic regions
* Visualize customer satisfaction levels
* Build a clean, modern, and intuitive dashboard

